### ===== FILE TRACKING APIs =====

### Create a new file upload record
POST http://localhost:3003/file-tracking
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "publicId": "public123",
  "fileUrl": "https://example.com/uploads/file123.jpg",
  "fileName": "file123.jpg",
  "fileType": "image/jpeg",
  "fileSize": 1024000,
  "folder": "uploads",
  "mimeType": "image/jpeg",
  "referenceCount": 1,
  "isTemporary": false,
  "isOrphaned": false,
  "uploadedByUserId": 1,
  "tags": ["product", "image"],
  "metadata": {
    "width": 1920,
    "height": 1080
  }
}

### Get all file upload records
GET http://localhost:3003/file-tracking

### Get file upload record by ID
GET http://localhost:3003/file-tracking/1

### Get file upload record by Public ID
GET http://localhost:3003/file-tracking/public/public123

### Update a file upload record
PATCH http://localhost:3003/file-tracking/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "referenceCount": 2
}

### Delete a file upload record
DELETE http://localhost:3003/file-tracking/1

### Get orphaned files
GET http://localhost:3003/file-tracking/orphaned

### Mark file for deletion
PATCH http://localhost:3003/file-tracking/1/mark-for-deletion

### Get files marked for deletion
GET http://localhost:3003/file-tracking/marked-for-deletion